sudo emerge --update --deep --with-bdeps=y --newuse world
</pre>



   </p><ul> <li>I get notified that some newer version package is required, so I have to manually install those package and re-run the `emerge world` </li> <li>Some package is gone (libreoffice-bin, for example). </li> </ul>   <p> Here is command to manually install package: </p>   


<pre class="prettyprint ">

sudo ebuild /usr/portage/www-client/firefox-bin/firefox-bin-23.0.ebuild unpack compile install qmerge clean
</pre>



